    {
      "id": "E:note:row328226:1",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "Chief Complaint:  Severe abdominal pain    HPI:    44 yr with recent diagnosis o",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row328226#s1",
      "text": "Chief Complaint:  Severe abdominal pain    HPI:    44 yr with recent diagnosis of mullerian adenocarcinoma presented to    [**Hospital1 54**] ER on [**2165-7-16**] with severe abdominal pain and vomiting."
    },
    {
      "id": "E:note:row328226:2",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "CT scan    revealed large pelvic mass with peritoneal spread and high grade smal",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row328226#s2",
      "text": "CT scan    revealed large pelvic mass with peritoneal spread and high grade small    bowel obstruction."
    },
    {
      "id": "E:note:row328226:3",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "Pt underwent ultrasound guided drainage. cytology final report from the    ultra",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row328226#s3",
      "text": "Pt underwent ultrasound guided drainage. cytology final report from the    ultrasound guided drainage showed neoplastic cells consistent with    mullerian adenocarcinoma."
    },
    {
      "id": "E:note:row328226:4",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "CT scan and MRI demonstrated extensive    disease.",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row328226#s4",
      "text": "CT scan and MRI demonstrated extensive    disease."
    },
    {
      "id": "E:note:row328226:5",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "Patient underwent TAH BSO with small bowel and sigmoid resection and    omentect",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row328226#s5",
      "text": "Patient underwent TAH BSO with small bowel and sigmoid resection and    omentectomy [**7-18**]  and intermittently required neo gtt. remained    intubated post op for airway protection r/t large doses of narcotics    given."
    },
    {
      "id": "E:note:row328226:6",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "Tachycardia, Other    Assessment:    ST 120s-130s  BP 100s-110s, cvp 3-5, tmax 9",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row328226#s6",
      "text": "Tachycardia, Other    Assessment:    ST 120s-130s  BP 100s-110s, cvp 3-5, tmax 99.3    Action:    Sedation increased, fent@125 and versed26. 500cc LR bolus x2 and 1L LR    bolusx1 given, EKG done,    D-Dimer sent."
    },
    {
      "id": "E:note:row328226:7",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "Response:    Remains tachy, BP stable, cvp 8-10, pt sedated and appears comforta",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row328226#s7",
      "text": "Response:    Remains tachy, BP stable, cvp 8-10, pt sedated and appears comfortable."
    },
    {
      "id": "E:note:row328226:8",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "Plan:    Cont to monitor, ?PE    Pain control (acute pain, chronic pain)    Asse",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row328226#s8",
      "text": "Plan:    Cont to monitor, ?PE    Pain control (acute pain, chronic pain)    Assessment:    Sedated on arrival to MICU, pt alert and nodding yes to pain, pain    controlled w/ boluses on fent and versed."
    },
    {
      "id": "E:note:row328226:9",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "Action:    Pt cont to be uncomfortable and becoming tachy, versed and fent gtts ",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
